mlbdata_5_team <- mlbdata %>%
            filter(name %in% c("Boston Red Sox", "New York Yankees", "Texas Rangers", "Detroit Tigers", "Atlanta Braves"), yearID >= 1999 & yearID <= 2017)

mlbdata_OPS_5_team <- mlbdata_5_team %>%
                                 mutate(OPS = (((H + X2B + 2*X3B + 3*HR)/AB) + ((H + BB + HBP)/(AB + BB + SF + HBP))))

mlbdata_BABIP_5_team <- mlbdata_5_team %>%
                                  mutate(BABIP = ((H-HR)/(AB-SO-HR+SF)))
library(ggplot2)
ggplot(mlbdata_OPS_5_team, aes(x= yearID, y = OPS, color= name)) + geom_line() + ggtitle("OPS by Year")
## Warning: Removed 5 rows containing missing values (geom_path).

ggplot(mlbdata_BABIP_5_team, aes(x= yearID, y = BABIP, color= name)) + geom_line() + ggtitle("Babip by Year")

ops vs win pct

library(dplyr)
mlbdata_2000 <- mlbdata %>% 
                filter(yearID == 2000) %>%
                                          mutate(OPS =(((H + X2B + 2*X3B + 3*HR)/AB) + ((H + BB + HBP)/(AB + BB + SF + HBP)))) %>%
                                          mutate(WP = W/G)
mlbdata_2007 <- mlbdata %>% 
                        filter(yearID == 2007) %>%
                        mutate(OPS =(((H + X2B + 2*X3B + 3*HR)/AB) + ((H + BB + HBP)/(AB + BB + SF + HBP)))) %>%
                        mutate(WP = W/G)
mlbdata_2015 <- mlbdata %>% 
                filter(yearID == 2015) %>%
                 mutate(OPS =(((H + X2B + 2*X3B + 3*HR)/AB) + ((H + BB + HBP)/(AB + BB + SF + HBP)))) %>%
                 mutate(WP = W/G)

library(ggplot2)

ggplot(mlbdata_2000, aes(x= OPS, y = WP)) + geom_point() + geom_smooth(method = lm) + ggtitle("OPS/WP 2000")

ggplot(mlbdata_2007, aes(x= OPS, y = WP)) + geom_point() + geom_smooth(method = lm) + ggtitle("OPS/WP 2007")

ggplot(mlbdata_2015, aes(x= OPS, y = WP)) + geom_point() + geom_smooth(method = lm) + ggtitle("OPS/WP 2015")

Babip vs win pct

mlbdata_2000_BvWP <- mlbdata %>% 
                    filter(yearID == 2000) %>%
                    mutate(BABIP = ((H-HR)/(AB-SO-HR+SF))) %>%
                   mutate(WP = W/G)

mlbdata_2007_BvWP <- mlbdata %>% 
                      filter(yearID == 2007) %>%
                      mutate(BABIP = ((H-HR)/(AB-SO-HR+SF))) %>%
                      mutate(WP = W/G)

mlbdata_2015_BvWP <- mlbdata %>% 
                    filter(yearID == 2015) %>%
                     mutate(BABIP = ((H-HR)/(AB-SO-HR+SF))) %>%
                    mutate(WP = W/G)

library(ggplot2)

ggplot(mlbdata_2000_BvWP, aes(x= BABIP, y = WP)) + geom_point() + geom_smooth(method = lm) + ggtitle("BABIP/WP 2000")

ggplot(mlbdata_2007_BvWP, aes(x= BABIP, y = WP)) + geom_point() + geom_smooth(method = lm) + ggtitle("BABIP/WP 2007")

ggplot(mlbdata_2015_BvWP, aes(x= BABIP, y = WP)) + geom_point() + geom_smooth(method = lm) + ggtitle("BABIP/WP 2015")
